@startuml Runtime Diagram
title Runtime Diagram - Neulogovani Korisnik

actor "Neulogovani korisnik" as Guest
participant "Frontend Router" as Router
participant "DesktopGate" as Gate
participant "LandingPage" as Landing
participant "SidebarMenu" as Menu
participant "Desktop Notice View" as Notice
participant "Auth stranice" as Auth

Guest -> Router: Otvara /
Router -> Gate: Provera sirine viewport-a

alt Desktop sirina
  Gate -> Landing: Render javne pocetne stranice
  Landing -> Menu: Prikaz stavki (Pocetna, Registracija, Prijava)
  Landing --> Guest: Hero + funkcionalnosti + CTA
else Manja sirina od desktop praga
  Gate -> Notice: Render poruke "Aplikacija je samo za desktop"
  Notice --> Guest: Prikaz ogranicenog ekrana
end

Guest -> Menu: Klik na Registracija
Menu -> Router: Navigacija na /registracija
Router -> Auth: Render registracione stranice

Guest -> Menu: Klik na Prijava
Menu -> Router: Navigacija na /prijava
Router -> Auth: Render stranice za prijavu

@enduml
